Johanssen, Christopher George Marquette. Reviewed by Stephen
Holden.
</P>
<P>
   REALESTATE-BOOK-REVIEW (Undated) _ Sex and real estate? For many
aging baby boomers, the scholar Marjorie Garber argues in her new
book, ``Sex and Real Estate,'' real estate now occupies the place
in their brains once reserved for sex: they fantasize not about the
perfect mate, but about parquet floors and 12-foot ceilings.
Reviewed by Michiko Kakutani.
</P>
<P>
   TV-WEEKEND (Undated) _ Julie Salamon spotlights the weekend
television fare: On Showtime, ``One Kill.''
</P>
