reshuffling and de-emphasis of San Francisco in the wake of its
merger with NationsBank, Bank of America has announced it will
reunite its northern and southern California divisions into a
single unit, with a Los Angeles-based executive heading the state
operation. By CHRISTIAN BERTHELSEN.
