International (MITI) is a group of mothers who believe that prayer
makes a difference. Individual chapters consisting of of two or
more moms meet once a week to pray for their children and the
schools they attend. Members believe that prayer is a way to
surround children with a spiritual presence even while they're at
school. (Dayton Daily News). 15. WITH PHOTOS.
