<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-04 13:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2741 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r p BC-CONDOLEEZA-CABINET-HN     08-04 1109
