<P>
   LEISURE-STUDIES (Undated) _ In the battle for respect, few
college students face more obstacles than the ``leisure studies''
majors. But the major is taking off as more and more students chase
careers in the recreation industry or simply prefer learning
outdoors. By David Abel. 1300 words.
</P>
<P>
   LOBSTER-BOATS (Southwest Harbor, Maine) _ The hard-working
lobster boat is rising above its humble origins as more people are
turning them into comfortable motor yachts. By Sam Allis. 1630
words. PHOTO
</P>
