   VENNOCHI-COLUMN (Philadelphia) _ Watching just a tiny piece of
that all-American enterprise _ the buying of the president _ leaves
the impression that most everything else that is happening here is
just circus. By Joan Vennochi. (Sent Thursday night.)
</P>
<P>
