<P>
   BUSH _ PITTSBURGH _ George W. Bush and Dick Cheney kick off a
post-convention barnstorming tour of key Midwestern states.
(Heath).
</P>
<P>
   WAN: Location Austin, category National, subcategory Politics
</P>
<P>
   POL-TICKER _ A brief roundup of the day's campaign events,
pulled from Cox staff and wire reports. (Cox News Service) ETA: 6
p.m.
