<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Adds Bush-Psyche)  
 For Release SUNDAY, August 6, 2000
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Boston Globe plans to move the following SUNDAY COLUMNS, in
advance, for use by NYTimes News Service clients.
