before you have to strip it all off before putting down a new
surface? By Peter Hotton.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   WARSH-COLUMN (Undated) _ In handling the GOP's Extremists so
effectively, George W. Bush set forth a vision of the Republican
party as he wants it to be eight years from now, not the way it is
today. It may get him a chance to make it so. Before passing on to
the Democrats, let's take a look at how the Losers spent the week.
By David Warsh. 1100 words.
</P>
