A legal team headed by Florida attorney Willie Gary is trying to
get the judge in the case to compel another team headed by
Washington attorney Cyrus Mehri to turn over its files on
plaintiffs who left Mehri to be represented by Gary. The judge may
rule. (This battle is unrelated to the $1.5 billion suit Gary has
filed against Coke on behalf of four women employees.) (Rankin,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
