Jersey couple whose 6-year-old son suffered brain damage in a 1997
store accident. According to the Philadelphia Inquirer, Brandon
Ryan was struck by at lease one of nine 20-pound boxes that fell
eight feet from a shelf. The settlement includes $100,000 for the
father, James Ryan, who suffered emotional distress after
witnessing the accident. (Bond, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 6.
