<P>
   SENIORS-COLUMN (Undated) _ Books aimed at the growing, and
increasingly affluent, senior market are steadily filling bookstore
shelves around the country. By Fed Brock.
</P>
<P>
   MONEY&AMP;MEDICINE-COLUMN (Undated) _ It is a familiar sequence of
events to anyone who has spent much time in a doctor's office. You
have blood taken, you call for the results, you get on with your
life _ and then weeks, months or even years later, you receive a
bill from the laboratory or explanation-of-benefits letter from
your insurance company. These missives can be maddening. By
Jennifer Steinhauer.
